text:
035 Nicky Jam 
The 2017 Billboard Latin Music Awards finalists were announced today (Feb. 7) and leading the list is Nicky Jam who's up for artist of the year and Hot Latin Song of the year. The Billboard Latin Music Awards are the culmination of the Billboard Latin Music Conference, taking place April 24-27 in Miami. In celebration of the announcement, below you can relive memorable moments from last year's Billboard Latin Music Conference and awards ceremony.
